result.name: 葡匯咪走雞葡國餐廳。 Mike's Chicken Comida de Portugal

reviews.text: Fabulous Portuguese Macau cuisine,  great service and very suitable for gathering of friends over some good food and wine etc. Price is middle to high but the taste is good, so it is justifiable for the pricing.

Super good food and good service there!
Very good roasted pork. Some of my friends are vegetarians and they have some good vegi. 

Nice dessert as well.
We all happy for dinner there. 😊😊😊

My relatives suggested that I go there to try out their Portuguese food. A Macanese friend of theirs recommended them to try it and, boy, it definitely didn't disappoint. 

From their sardines and ox tail stew to their suckling pig which we pre-booked, everything was to my heart's content. I will definitely bookmark this place and come again when I can.

Yummy food, perfect for big groups like family or friends gathering. Staffs were attentive and food is delicious and above standard. Personal fav was their baked chicken and prawns! Desserts are very pretty and perfect for photo taking.

Found this restaurant by chance. It serves Portuguese cuisine or some version of it. The service was excellent. The staff were friendly and attentive. We had the special menu for two persons; snack platter (bacalhau crochets, chicken, squid rings), whole chicken (half piri-piri, half garlic), cabbage bacalhau soup, etc. I really enjoyed it. I think I may come back again next time. The red sangria was also pretty good.

result.name: 葡匯咪走雞葡國餐廳。 Mike's Chicken Comida de Portugal

reviews.text: 部份午市價格倘可接受,當日食葡國雞飯D汁味道適中,有D甜味，似係椰汁,可能係果亞菜式，但上菜時間就耐得很,等成半個鐘至上到菜,好慢好慢。

Fabulous Portuguese Macau cuisine,  great service and very suitable for gathering of friends over some good food and wine etc. Price is middle to high but the taste is good, so it is justifiable for the pricing.

Super good food and good service there!
Very good roasted pork. Some of my friends are vegetarians and they have some good vegi. 

Nice dessert as well.
We all happy for dinner there. 😊😊😊

好久沒有過大海賭錢，亦十分懷念葡國餐，因此今天相約有人於尖沙咀美麗華商場，在這一間葡國餐廳一聚。
餐廳位於地鐵站附近，相約10分鐘路程。餐廳的寧靜環境與尖沙咀大街吵吵鬧鬧的感覺截然不同， 十分舒服。
一進餐廳很有葡萄牙國家的感覺，不同的相片和國旗令你恍如置身葡萄牙一樣。
這裏的食物亦相當有葡國風味，例如馬介休球，胡椒蝦，乳豬和烤雞等，都煮得非常出色。
值得一提的是，這裏的飲品和甜品都非常不錯。濃縮咖啡是外國進口，非常濃烈。乾冰雪糕更是一絕，味道非常美味愛賣相亦非常有趣，值得一試。

點了數道菜， 例如炸馬介休球，里斯本沙律， 葡式多士， 葡式胡椒蝦， 白汁燴雞和乳豬。
炸馬介休球熱辣辣，香噴噴， 口感外脆內軟並帶有一陣不知名香料味。
葡式多士用芝士鋪面再加以烘焙而成， 每啖都是濃濃芝士味。
葡式胡椒蝦以胡椒和白汁配上洋蔥製作而成， 店舖選用了海中蝦， 每一隻蝦都非常入味。
最驚喜是雪糕， 裝著雪糕的玻璃器皿下放置了乾冰， 店員把水倒在乾冰， 之後一場乾冰匯演盛放而出！
